### Variables — set before running
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@adminAccessToken = REPLACE_ME

### 1) Admin login (example — adjust body to your admin credentials)
# POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/auth/login
# Content-Type: application/json
#
# {
#   "email": "admin@example.com",
#   "password": "your-password"
# }

### 2) Create demo property (uses create-demo-property.json next to this file)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/properties
Authorization: Bearer {{adminAccessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

< ./create-demo-property.json
